subject: Re: World Customs Organization  Of
body:
Hello there, 

I'm glad to hear from you. I hope you're doing well too. It's interesting to hear about the work of the World Customs Of United States Border Patrol. Can you tell me more about what your role involves? 

As for the details you asked for, I'm sorry but I don't feel comfortable sharing personal information online. However, I'd love to continue our conversation and learn more about your work.

Also, could you explain a bit more about the ATM card and gift cards? How are they related to your work?

Looking forward to hearing from you soon!

Best wishes,
Helen
